# This file is intentionally empty.
# stage0/prerun.sh uses --no-check-gpg with debootstrap because
# the Raspberry Pi GPG key cannot be downloaded inside Docker
# (Cloudflare protection on raspberrypi.com). The build boots from
# pure Debian (deb.debian.org) and does not need RPi keys at this stage.
# RPi packages are handled by stage1/ packages and apt configuration.